  Accounts
  Choose an account, auth flow, or fork setting.
  This session: Account 1 (pro)
  Shared active account: Account 2 (pro)
  2 misnamed account file(s) can be renamed; 1 duplicate file(s) are ignored.

› 1. Login with ChatGPT               Start browser login and wait for the callback.
  2. Login with device code           Show a one-time code for browser sign-in.
  3. Add API key                      Enter an API key and make it the active account.
  4. Switch account                   4 saved account(s) available.
  5. Switch to shared active account  Adopt shared active account Account 2 (pro).
  6. Remove account                   Delete a saved auth blob from ~/.codex/.accounts/.
  7. Rename account files             3 misnamed file(s) are ignored until renamed.
  8. View account limits              View latest usage and reset times. 2 refresh due.

  1 more option(s) below. Press ↓ to see them.
  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
